install steps ubuntu 24.04

update 

setup task_bar

create sudo   users    --> 	newuser
create normal users    --> 	sanaya, nosuser(non open source apps), guest

set up flatpak and install non open source apps only for nosuser user

login with nosuser user and install flatseal and non open source apps

setup firefox	(book-mark gmail, drive, github, chatgpt, youtube) 

install gimp app image

mount partition for all users 
	open disks, edit mount options
		turn off     -->  user session defaults,  
		tick options -->  mount at startup and show in user interface
		mount point  -->  /media/data directory
	sudo   setfacl   -m    u:newuser:rwx    /media/data

install qemu kvm

install git	(copy directory ~/.ssh and repos)

